OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Journalist Maral
OL,7,FShafafy
OL,9,FFor more than 56 days now, Iranians
OL,10,Fhave been living under one of the
OL,11,Flongest national internet shutdowns in
OL,12,Fhistory, cutting off communication
OL,13,Fwith the outside world for
OL,14,Fapproximately 93 million people and
OL,15,Ffor many, destroying livelihoods that
OL,16,Frelied heavily on the digital world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"I still can't clearly separate which
OL,7,Fwas harder, being under bombardment or
OL,8,Fthe internet shutdown," says Hedieh
OL,9,F(pseudonym), who left Iran after the
OL,10,Fceasefire. Working in the creative
OL,11,Fsector, her job was suspended as soon
OL,12,Fas the shutdown was implemented.
OL,14,F"We didn't even have access to our
OL,15,Ffiles. The studio I work with was
OL,16,Fentirely suspended. On top of that, I
OL,17,Flost a project I had with an
OL,18,Finternational client because it became
OL,19,Fcompletely impossible to communicate,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]vD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"Think about what that does to a
OL,7,Fperson mentally, you can't work, you
OL,8,Fcan't communicate with anyone, at the
OL,9,Fsame time there's a war...its violence
OL,10,Fcan be even greater than that of
OL,11,Fbombs, though it is a silent kind of
OL,12,Fviolence," she added.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
