OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FAccording to calculations by
OL,7,FFactnameh, a factchecking platform
OL,8,Ffocused on Persianlanguage news, the
OL,9,Fcurrent internet shutdown is costing
OL,10,FIran an estimated $40 million per day.
OL,11,FFifty-six days into the current
OL,12,Fshutdown, that damage now exceeds
OL,13,F$2.5bn.
OL,15,F"I haven't seen anyone not impacted,"
OL,16,Fsaid Darius (pseudonym), speaking to
OL,17,Fme from Tehran. He's one of the small
OL,18,Fpercentage of Iranians able to access
OL,19,Fthe internet using either a Starlink
OL,20,Fdevice or expensive VPNs.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FDarius' business, an internet service
OL,7,Fhe's invested almost a million dollars
OL,8,Fin over the past 8 years, is going
OL,9,Fbankrupt, and he's having to lay off
OL,10,Fover 75% of his staff. "It's just
OL,11,Fimpossible to stay afloat, you know?
OL,12,FBecause of the cost of the crisis, one
OL,13,Fafter another, and then the nail in
OL,14,Fthe coffin was these three different
OL,15,Fepisodes of internet shutdown."
OL,26,@rD@XOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
