OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FThe Islamic Republic of Iran has a
OL,7,Fhistory of shutting down the internet
OL,8,Fduring times of conflict and uprising
OL,9,Fin the country. From 2019, when
OL,10,Fprotests broke out in the country over
OL,11,Frising fuel costs, to the Woman, Life,
OL,12,FFreedom protests of 2023 and the 12-
OL,13,Fday war with Israel last year,
OL,14,Fauthorities have been using the
OL,15,Fmeasure, they say, for national
OL,16,Fsecurity reasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FBut a succession of recent crises,
OL,7,Ffrom protests in January to the
OL,8,Foutbreak of war at the end of
OL,9,FFebruary, means Iranians have spent 76
OL,10,Fof the past 114 days without proper
OL,11,Faccess to the internet. With inflation
OL,12,Fexceeding 50% in 2025, there is
OL,13,Fgrowing fear and desperation about the
OL,14,Flong-term economic impact of this on
OL,15,Fpeople across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FParnia, who lives in the UK, has only
OL,7,Fbeen able to speak with her mum and
OL,8,Fsister three times since the outbreak
OL,9,Fof war. From an upper-middle-class
OL,10,Fbackground in Shiraz, she's never been
OL,11,Fconcerned about her family's financial
OL,12,Fsituation until now.
OL,14,F"Now I've been hearing my mom saying,
OL,15,F'don't worry about us, we are still
OL,16,Fable to buy meat, fruits'. That's just
OL,17,Fshocking. I mean, I never thought I'm
OL,18,Fgonna hear that from my mom," she
OL,19,Fsaid. "I always thought we were in
OL,20,Fthat margin of comfortable, with
OL,21,Fspending money for at least basics."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@]O]{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FParnia's sister used to run an online
OL,7,Fshop selling her own handmade objects.
OL,8,FShe spent the last few years building
OL,9,Fher business from the ground up,
OL,10,Ftaking part in classes to learn how to
OL,11,Fgrow her audience online.
OL,13,FBut the internet shutdown has
OL,14,Fcompletely collapsed sales, and she
OL,15,Fand her husband are now relying on
OL,16,FParnia's mum's retirement money for
OL,17,Fsurvival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"There is more pressure on my mum to
OL,7,Fprovide for them and to support them.
OL,8,FHer husband is also a fantastic,
OL,9,Fskilful person, but because of the
OL,10,Fsituation, there's no money in the
OL,11,Fconstruction industry," she said. "My
OL,12,Fmum is now in a position where she is
OL,13,Fhaving to provide for not only for
OL,14,Fherself getting older, and more health
OL,15,Fneeds, but also for her adult
OL,16,Fchildren. They are over 40."
OL,18,FThe lack of means of communication
OL,19,Fmeans Parnia isn't even able to
OL,20,Fsupport them in the ways that she
OL,21,Fnormally would be able to.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@WO]sD@cOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"I got several messages from my
OL,7,Fextended family desperate for money
OL,8,Ffor basic things, but I wasn't able to
OL,9,Fhelp. In normal days, I would find a
OL,10,Fway to send them money, but because of
OL,11,Fthe communication situation, I can't,"
OL,12,Fshe said.
OL,14,FWhile this is not the first time the
OL,15,FIslamic Republic has shut down the
OL,16,Finternet, there are growing concerns
OL,17,Fthat the current prolonged blackout
OL,18,Fcould be used to further entrench a
OL,19,Fsystem of tiered web access that has
OL,20,Fbeen gradually rolled out in recent
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
