OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FEarlier this month, the Minister of
OL,7,FInformation and Communications
OL,8,FTechnology of Iran, Sattar Hashemi,
OL,9,Foutlined aspects of these plans in an
OL,10,Fop-ed for Shargh newspaper,
OL,11,Fintroducing one of the first products
OL,12,Ftied to the initiative: "Internet
OL,13,FPro." Users must meet specific
OL,14,Feligibility criteria and submit
OL,15,Fpersonal information to apply.
OL,17,FDepending on approval, they are
OL,18,Fgranted varying levels of access to
OL,19,Fwebsites and apps, access that is
OL,20,Ffully monitored and traceable.
OL,26,@tD@YOUuD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FFarzaneh Badiei, founder of Digital
OL,7,FMedusa, an organisation that focuses
OL,8,Fon digital governance, describes the
OL,9,Fsituation as a "digital apartheid".
OL,11,F"These are all speculations. We are
OL,12,Fhoping that access to the internet is
OL,13,Frestored, but the situation looks very
OL,14,Fgrim at the moment," she said.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@bO]sD@AOUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"If it happens that they do not
OL,7,Frestore the internet and we have this
OL,8,Ftiered system, we are going to see
OL,9,Fpeople who are much poorer, and much
OL,10,Fmore oppressed," she warned. "It's not
OL,11,Fjust like a matter of sharing
OL,12,Finformation online, this is a matter
OL,13,Fof having access to health information
OL,14,Fand having access to educational
OL,15,Fmaterials."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@PO]rD@^O]wD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,FThe growing desperation to connect to
OL,7,Fthe outside world and the frustration
OL,8,Fof being denied that basic access are
OL,9,Fintensifying the already intense
OL,10,Fatmosphere of oppression in Iran, with
OL,11,Fauthorities arresting individuals for
OL,12,Fpurchasing illegal VPNs or using
OL,13,FStarlink devices.
OL,15,FShayan, who has worked as both a
OL,16,Fdigital activist and an IT consultant
OL,17,Fin Iran and left only last year for
OL,18,Fhis own safety, said: "It's exactly
OL,19,Flike a digital hostage taking.
OL,26,@zD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"If you want to explain it to someone,
OL,7,Fyou can say, we're putting you on an
OL,8,Fisland, which is surrounded by the
OL,9,Fmilitary, they tell you if you move,
OL,10,Fwe'll shoot you, and we're not giving
OL,11,Fyou any means to communicate with the
OL,12,Foutside world. And you have to stay
OL,13,Fhere until we tell you."
OL,15,FCould a continued internet shutdown
OL,16,Ffuel further unrest in Iran, amid
OL,17,Fmounting economic pressure and
OL,18,Fincreasing oppression?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"Yes, absolutely," said Farzaneh. "But
OL,7,Fat the moment, the regime is very
OL,8,Fcruel."There's a ceasefire, but we are
OL,9,Fin a war and the Iranian community is
OL,10,Fvery vulnerable. But in the future, I
OL,11,Fam hoping that because Iranians have
OL,12,Falways cared about access to the
OL,13,Finternet, I am hopeful that they can
OL,14,Fpush back and they can restore their
OL,15,Faccess."
OL,17,FHedieh is not as optimistic. "It's
OL,18,Freally serious," she said. "I can't
OL,19,Fpredict what will happen. People have
OL,20,Fbeen really suppressed, and it's post-
OL,21,Fwar; everyone has a kind of tiredness."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@RO]nD@cOUpD@GOUyD@^OUzD@PO]zD@
OL,26,A\OU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1777065070
OL,3,C'Silent violence': Life inside Iran's
OL,4,Cinternet blackout
OL,6,F"I think it's actually kept people in
OL,7,Fa kind of survival mode. People are
OL,8,Fworried after the war; the most basic
OL,9,Fthings are enough for them. Me,
OL,10,Fmyself, I don't have energy for change
OL,11,Fanymore. I just want the life back
OL,12,Fthat I've lost."
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
